Bonk!

You are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 2}.

Melee

Shot your Foot

Until healed, you are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} and take a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.other-effects.Item.Effect: -5-foot circumstance penalty to your land Speed]{-5-foot circumstance penalty to your land speed}.

Ranged

Overexertion

You are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Fatigued].

Unarmed

Side Effect

You are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}. You are also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} until healed.

Spell
